  "title": "12 Months Finance Assistant (Up to $4,000) #BTS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Daily entry of receipts into accounting system</li><li>Handle and manage Accounts Receivables and Accounts payable Functions</li><li>Update and maintain accounting journals</li><li>Ensure entries are charged to the correct account codes</li><li>Handle customer's queries on the daily financial transactional activities</li><li>Generate monthly accounts receivables report</li><li>Perform analysis of accounts, preparation of audit schedules etc</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 1 to 2 years of experience in Accounting Functions</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to meganng@recruitexpress.com.sg<br /><strong>Attention to: Megan Ng Su Ting (CEI: R23115059)</strong><br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />EA No. 99C4599<br /><br />*** We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
